\tau & =\left(f\left(\sqrt{x_{i}}\right)+g\left(\sqrt{x_{i}}\right)\right)-\left(f\left(\sqrt{x_{i}^{0}}\right)+g\left(\sqrt{x_{i}^{0}}\right)\right)\equiv F_{1}\left(x_{i};x_{i}^{0}\right)\\
