.
 Thus, 
\begin_inset Formula $m\geq1$
\end_inset

.
 Note that 
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

 is proportional to the internal energy contribution from the distortion.
 From 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:StretchODESystem"

